    dc:creator "Jaiswara, Ranjana; Desutter-Grandcolas, Laure" ;
    dc:date "2014" ;
    dc:title "Revision of the genus Pteroplistes in India, with the description of two new species Pteroplistes kervasae Jaiswara, n. sp. and Pteroplistes masinagudi Jaiswara, n. sp. (Orthoptera, Grylloidea, Pteroplistinae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.227312>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.227314>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.227311> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.227312>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Pteroplistes species: (A – C) Maxillary palpi joints of (A) P. masinagudi Jaiswara n. sp. (B) P. platycleis Bolivar, 1900 (1899), (C) P. kervasae Jaiswara n. sp.; (D – F, L, M) Male and female FWs of (D) P. platycleis Bolivar, 1900 (1899), female, (E, F) P. kervasae Jaiswara n. sp. male and female, (L, M) P. masinagudi Jaiswara n. sp. male and female; (G, K) male supra anal plates of (G) P. kervasae Jaiswara n. sp. and (K) P. masinagudi Jaiswara n. sp.; (H, N) male subgenital plates of (H) of P. kervasae Jaiswara n. sp. in dorsal (i) and lateral view (ii), (N) of P. masinagudi Jaiswara n. sp. in dorsal (i) and lateral view (ii); (J, O) subgenital plate of females, (J) of P. kervasae Jaiswara n. sp. and (O) of P. masinagudi Jaiswara n. sp.; (I) female copulatory papilla ventral (i) and dorsal (ii) view of P. masinagudi Jaiswara n. sp." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/227312/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.227314>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Male genitalia in dorsal, ventral and lateral view of (A – C) P. kervasae Jaiswara n. sp.; (D – F) P. masinagudi Jaiswara n. sp. Abbreviations, see Material and Methods. Scale 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/227314/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.227311>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Pteroplistes species from Western Ghats, India. (A) P. platycleis Bolivar, 1900 (1899), (B – C) P. kervasae Jaiswara n. sp. male and female, (D – E) P. masinagudi Jaiswara n. sp. male and female. Scale 5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/227311/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

